Class BatchedCsvStream.BatchSpliterator

    private static class BatchedCsvStream.BatchSpliterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Spliterator<java.lang.String[]>
    The internal batching Spliterator implementation. This does all the magic of splitting the stream into "jobs" that each cpu core can handle.
